      <section eId="sec_CHC-424-5">
        <num>CHC 424.5</num>
        <heading>424.5. Â CASA; appearance; witness</heading>
        <subsection eId="CHC-424-5__subsec_A">
          <num>A.</num>
          <content>
            <p>The CASA volunteer shall be entitled to attend all court proceedings and hearings of any kind pertaining to a child for whom he is assigned.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CHC-424-5__subsec_B">
          <num>B.</num>
          <content>
            <p>The CASA volunteer may be called as a witness in the proceedings by any party or by the court and may request of the court the opportunity to appear as a witness.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=73168</p>
        </authorialNote>
      </section>
